sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / SDK
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant OAuth as oauth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant UI as ds-pipeline-ui<br/>3000/TCP HTTP
    participant API as ds-pipeline<br/>(API Server)<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant MySQL as MySQL/MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP
    participant MinIO as MinIO/S3<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Tekton as Tekton Pipelines
    participant PA as ds-pipeline-<br/>persistenceagent
    participant SWF as ds-pipeline-<br/>scheduledworkflow
    participant MW as metadata-writer
    participant Envoy as metadata-envoy<br/>9090/TCP gRPC
    participant MLMD as metadata-grpc<br/>8080/TCP gRPC

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission and Execution

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v1beta1/pipelines/upload<br/>HTTPS TLS (Reencrypt)
    Route->>OAuth: Forward<br/>OpenShift OAuth
    OAuth->>UI: Authenticated request<br/>HTTP/3000
    UI->>API: REST API call<br/>HTTP/8888
    API->>MySQL: Store pipeline metadata<br/>MySQL/3306<br/>Username/Password
    API->>MinIO: Store pipeline artifact<br/>HTTP/9000<br/>AccessKey/SecretKey
    User->>API: POST /apis/v1beta1/runs<br/>Bearer Token
    API->>K8s: Create PipelineRun CR<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s->>Tekton: PipelineRun created

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 2: Pipeline Run Status Sync

    PA->>K8s: Watch PipelineRuns/TaskRuns<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>PA: PipelineRun status update
    PA->>API: Report run status<br/>HTTP/8888

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 3: Scheduled Workflow Execution

    SWF->>K8s: Watch ScheduledWorkflow CRs<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>SWF: ScheduledWorkflow trigger
    SWF->>K8s: Create PipelineRun<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 4: ML Metadata Tracking

    MW->>K8s: Watch PipelineRuns<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>MW: PipelineRun completion
    MW->>Envoy: Write metadata<br/>gRPC/9090<br/>plaintext
    Envoy->>MLMD: Forward<br/>gRPC/8080<br/>plaintext
    MLMD->>MySQL: Store ML metadata<br/>MySQL/3306<br/>Username/Password
